flowchart TB
    U[用户/商户] --> G[网关与幂等层]
    G --> O[订单服务]
    O --> ODB[(订单库)]
    O --> OE[(ORDER_EVENT_NORMAL)]
    O --> OF[(ORDER_STATE_FIFO)]
    O --> OD[(ORDER_CLOSE_DELAY)]

    PAY[支付回调] --> PS[支付服务]
    PS --> PDB[(支付库)]
    PS --> PT[(PAYMENT_RESULT_TXN)]
    PT --> OS[订单状态服务]
    OS --> ODB
    OS --> OF

    OE --> SEARCH[搜索投影组]
    OE --> BI[实时数据组]
    PT --> LEDGER[账务组]
    PT --> POINTS[积分组]
    PT --> INVOICE[发票组]
    OF --> NOTIFY[通知编排组]
    OD --> CLOSE[超时关闭组]

    subgraph RocketMQ多可用区集群
